abstract: Enrique Marquez is indicted on charges including conspiracy to provide material support to terrorist for providing weapons to San Bernardino, Calif, shooter Syed Rizwan Farook.
lead_paragraph: The indictment, on charges including conspiracy and lying about gun purchases, supersedes similar charges filed against Enrique Marquez two weeks ago.

headline.main: Federal Grand Jury Indicts Friend in San Bernardino Massacre
headline.print_headline: Federal Grand Jury Indicts Friend in California Massacre
